column3: Young Dolph’s partner Mia Jaye took to social media on Thursday night about a day after the Memphis rapper was fatally shot to thank people for sending prayers.

column3: Will spoke about the showdown during a recent interview on 'Sway in the Morning.' But he didn't seem that confident in his catalog: L is going body me.

column1: Judge Deems Prison 'Inappropriate' for Man Who Sexually Assaulted 4 Teenage Girls
